- US Federal reserve
  http://www.federalreserve.gov/releases/H10/Update/h10daily.txt
- PACIFIC Exchange Rate Service
  http://fx.sauder.ubc.ca/today.html
- Bank of Canada
  http://www.bankofcanada.ca/en/financial_markets/csv/exchange_eng.csv

